					<h2>Character Background</h2>
					<p>Born Claire Farron, "Lightning" is the main protagonist in Final Fantasy VIII.  
						She tries to save her younger sister, Serah, who was turned into a I'Clie, 
						only to become one herself.  Lightning is a determined and intense character 
						with a cold, standoffish personality.</p>
